reviews.review_text:
Oh my... I love this site, just for the gems you'll find all the time!

Download this just for the Saint of Circumstance.

You won't regret it.
Hissy and distant Warning - tape hiss and the recording sounds very distant and lacks fidelity.  Not for those who like their GD loud and clear.
